===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|gladere|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{term|glædra|pos=adj|lang=ang}}, {{term|glador|pos=adverb|lang=ang}}, comparative of {{term|glæd||glad, shining, bright|lang=ang}}. More at {{l|en|glad}}.

