'''gladder'''

# {{comparative of|glad}}

===Etymology 2===
From {{etyl|enm}} {{term|glader|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|ang}} {{recons|gladere|gladere|gladder|lang=ang}}, from {{term|gladian||to make glad|lang=ang}}, equivalent to {{suffix|glad|er}}.

